My first look inside the game was amazing! Everything looked so realistic, and animals were great to hunt. However, I don't enjoy not having any locked screen, like Gluten Free Games' former apps. A great improvement from the original, but still pretty glitchy and hard to play rn. The camera switches from locked and free mode with no warning, so navigating and hunting is hard. Still many bugs but i appreciate your effort on trying to fix all of this and for a newly released game, it was understandable. But overall another great game from you, keep it up! I hope you also make an ultimate lion revamped in the future.
